OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy today with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain and drizzle where the cloud
OL,7,Fthickens. Low cloud will bring some
OL,8,Ffog around hills and southern coasts.
OL,9,FA few brighter glimmers are possible
OL,10,Fin the afternoon in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLow cloud will continue to
OL,13,Fbring showery outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fovernight, and some fog over the hills
OL,15,Ftoo. Staying frost free under the
OL,16,Fblanket of cloud.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA cloudy and grey start with
OL,19,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
