OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FPatchy
OL,6,Fcloud and sunny spells on Tuesday, and
OL,7,Fthe odd shower. Turning increasingly
OL,8,Fwindy thereafter with spells of rain
OL,9,Fand scattered showers, and some
OL,10,Fbrighter interludes too. Near normal
OL,11,Ftemperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
